Redis Server installation  in Linux distribution:

This downloads and install redis-server on the system
$ wget https://download.redis.io/releases/redis-6.2.5.tar.gz
$ tar xzf redis-6.2.5.tar.gz
$ cd redis-6.2.5
$ make
To run redis-server:
    $src/redis-server


Redis Server installation  in Windows:
 Download the msi from : https://github.com/MicrosoftArchive/redis/releases
 walk through the installer and complete the installation
 To run redis-server:
    redis-server --service-start

Run the script drivre.py using "python driver.py"
